Step 1 npx npm-check-updates -u

	this will give you list of packages for update according to 
	Major.Minor.Patch

	Remember Major and Minor will always break your application 99.9%
	Because of new implementations and syntax or deprecations

Step 2 npm i (to update and install new packages)

Step3 npm audit (to check Vulnerabilites

Step4 npm audit fix

Step5 Then start writing your server.
